Lots of excitement in the law enforcement community about AIC's Criminal Justice Master's Program!

The program's Gina Sanderson and CJ Degree Completion Coordinator Mike Stevens met with the Lawrence Police Department on July 30 to share the good news that graduates are now eligible for the Police Career Incentive Pay Program known as the Quinn Bill. AIC is proud to support officers in their career advancement!
